Employee Task Management Dashboard
Tech Stack: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Tailwind CSS, LocalStorage
- Built a responsive web app with Admin/Employee dashboards, improving task workflow efficiency by 30%.
- Enabled Admin task creation and Employee completion tracking, reducing manual effort by 25% and boosting accountability by 20%.
- Applied React + Tailwind CSS with LocalStorage persistence, delivering a modern UI and ~15% faster load times.
- Conducted usability testing and iterative refinements, ensuring a smooth user experience and recruiter‑friendly project showcase.
